<% content_for :head do %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "blasts.js.coffee" %>
<% end %>
<% provide(:title, 'Grapevine') %>

<div id="wantmore5">
  <!-- Restaurant: <%= @blast.name %> -->
        
    <div class="review-wrapper clearfix">
      <div class="review">
        
        <p class="the-review">&ldquo;<%= @blast.review_description %>&rdquo;</p>
        <p class="rating">Customer Rating: <strong><%= @blast.rating %> stars</strong></p>
        <p class="posted">Posted on: <%= @blast.review_dine_date %></p>
        <p class="opentable-logo"><%= image_tag 'pics/opentable-logo.png' %></p>
      </div>
      

      <div class="review-tag">
        <h2>Did you know about this review?</h2>
        <h3 class="purple">Can you respond to all of them?</h3>
        <!-- <p>Nullam id dolor id nibh ultricies vehicula ut id elit. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Maecenas faucibus mollis interdum.</p> -->
        <p class="other-logos"><%= image_tag 'pics/logo-yelp.gif', :class => 'yelp' %> <%= image_tag 'pics/Google-Places.jpg' %> <%= image_tag 'pics/bing-logo.png', :class => 'yahoo' %> <%= image_tag 'pics/logo_urbanspoon.png' %> <%= image_tag 'pics/citysearch-logo.png' %>
      </div><!-- /.review-tag -->
    </div><!-- /.review-wrapper -->

    <div class="reviews-matter col-wrapper clearfix">
      <h3>Why do Reviews Matter?</h3>

      <div class="col first">
        <h4>Diners Read Reviews</h4>
        <%= image_tag 'icons/icon-fork-spoon.png', :class => 'col-icon fork-spoon' %>
        <p>You already have a reputation before a diner walks through your door and today its even easier for your potential customer to gauge your restaurant.</p>
        <p>&ldquo;70% of potential diners read online reviews before selecting a restaurant.&rdquo; <br>- <em>Business Week</em></p>

      </div><!-- /.col -->

      <div class="col">
        <h4>Reviews Are Everywhere</h4>
        <%= image_tag 'icons/icon-star.png', :class => 'col-icon star' %>
        <p>Focusing on just one review website doesn&rsquo;t cut it anymore.</p>
        <p>&ldquo;There are over 6 million restaurant reviews online right now and that number is growing.&rdquo;<br> - <em>Entrepreneur.com</em></p>

      </div><!-- /.col -->

      <div class="col">
        <h4>Reviews Affect Profits</h4>
        <%= image_tag 'icons/icon-graph.png', :class => 'col-icon graph' %>
        <p>It can now be tracked just how much impact reviews have on your bottom line in the restaurant industry</p>
        <p>&ldquo;In 2011, a one star drop in review ratings resulted in an average of $8,393 in lost revenue for restaurants.&rdquo;<br>
                     - <em>National Restaurant Association</em></p>
        

      </div><!-- /.col -->
    </div><!-- /.col-wrapper -->

    <blockquote>

      <p><img src="http://flickholdr.com/80/80/headshot"> &ldquo;Vestibulum id ligula porta felis euismod semper. Curabitur blandit tempus porttitor.&rdquo; <span class="author">Peter North, Malibu Burger Shack</span></p>
    </blockquote>


    <div class="grapevine-helps col-wrapper clearfix">
      <h3>How does Grapevine help?</h3>

      <div class="col first">
        <h4>Track Major Review Sites</h4>
        <%= image_tag 'icons/icon-group.png', :class => 'col-icon group' %>
        <p>We monitor all the popular review sites across the web&mdash;including OpenTable, Yelp, TripAdvisor, UrbanSpoon, GoogleLocal, CitySearch, InsiderPages, YellowPages and more. If there is a review site we&rsquo;re not monitoring for you, contact us and we&rsquo;ll add it.</p>

      </div><!-- /.col -->

      <div class="col">
        <h4>Receive Email Notifications</h4>
        <%= image_tag 'icons/icon-email.png', :class => 'col-icon email' %>
        <p>Every day, people talk about your business online&mdash;sometimes good, sometimes not so much. It&rsquo;s tough to keep up with checking for new reviews each day - which is why we do it for you! If a new review pops up online, you&rsquo;ll get an email alert from us automatically.</p>

      </div><!-- /.col -->

      <div class="col">
        <h4>Save Time &amp; Energy</h4>
        <%= image_tag 'icons/icon-time.png', :class => 'col-icon time' %>
        <p>How much time does Grapevine save you?</p>
        <p><strong>10</strong> sites at <strong>2 mins</strong> per site = <strong>20 mins per day or 10 hours a month</strong>.</p>
        <p>Rather than spend time searching for reviews, we deliver them to you!</p>

      </div><!-- /.col -->

    </div><!-- /.col-wrapper -->

    <div class="signup-bar">
      <p class="last-tag">No service out there makes knowing what your customers are saying about your business as quick &amp; simple as <span class="purple">Grapevine</span>.</p>
      <a class="show-form purple_button btn">30 Day Free Trial - Sign Up Today</a>

    </div>
  

</div><!-- /#wantmore5 -->